description: EWPG Holding AB engages in the research, development, and manufacture of technology for turning ocean and sea waves into electricity. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2019-07-18. The firm develops technology for production of clean electricity from ocean and sea waves.
